stories.title: Lehmann stars as Zimbabwe collapse
stories.subTitle: Zimbabwe v Australia, 2nd ODI, Harare
stories.summary: It was never expected that any of the matches between Australia and the team supposedly representing Zimbabwe would be competitive: the only questions were how much the Aussies would win by, and whether the Zimbabweans could avoid total humiliation
